Lilly Pulitzer

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Lilly Pulitzer


Born
Lillian Lee McKim
(1931-11-10)November 10, 1931
Roslyn, New York, U.S.


Died
April 7, 2013(2013-04-07) (aged 81)
Palm Beach, Florida, U.S.


